<%= render "banner" %>

<div class="container text-center mt-4">

  <%# Bootstrap collapse %>
  <div style="padding-bottom: 30px">
    <h3 class="home-margin mb-5 home-h3">You may be asking yourself...</h3>

    <p class="mb-5 home-bootstrap">
      <a class="btn btn-flat mb-3" data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#multiCollapseExample1" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="multiCollapseExample1">Why do I need a mentor?</a>
      <button class="mb-3 mx-3 btn btn-flat" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#multiCollapseExample2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="multiCollapseExample2">Why should I become a mentor?</button>
    </p>

    <section>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col">
          <div class="collapse multi-collapse" id="multiCollapseExample1">
            <div class="card card-body">
              Mentors can help you grow a professional network by connecting you to others,
              they also serve as coaches that can help you during times of change and/or transition,
              challenging you, and pushing you to go farther than you thought you could go! Mentors can inspire you and keep you focused.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col">
          <div class="collapse multi-collapse" id="multiCollapseExample2">
            <div class=" card card-body">
              It's essential to broaden your horizons, by mentoring others you'll be working with a wide range of people and it is
              important that you are able to relate.
              Leadership is also a valuable skill in any environment, and mentoring is a key part of it.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</div>

